source.name: Vitiligo Natural Treatment
source.description: Vitiligo natural treatment is classified as medical, surgical, herbal therapies and homeopathic treatment. Very often medical and surgical therapies contain many side effects even skin cancer is also one of the most famous side effect of these therapies.
